summary: This mod adds some darkness and contrast to the exterior of the College of Winterhold. This does not alter the interior, just exterior, all buildings, bridges, and Mage Statue.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-s2qNEDCn4mo/UNzj-pNYEAI/AAAAAAAAAo4/m34KKqctedk/s800/dmcline.png[/img][/center]

This mod adds some darkness and contrast to the exterior of the College of Winterhold. This does not alter the interior, just exterior, all buildings, bridges, and Mage Statue. I believe it gives it a bit more of an \"aged\" feeling.
author: dmcthunder999
